channel.title: Course Textbooks :: K-State CIS 642/643 Textbook
channel.description: Web Only This textbook was authored for the CIS 642/643 - Software Engineering Project I&II course at Kansas State University. This front matter is specific to that course. If you are not enrolled in the course, please disregard this section. This course does not have a required print textbook. The resources presented in the modules are also organized into an online textbook that can be accessed here: https://textbooks.cs.ksu.edu/cis642-643/. You may find this a useful reference if you prefer a traditional textbook layout.
